Comment: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:50.97,chop,,0000,0000,0000,,【OP：瞳の中の迷宫】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:31.21,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}想要見你 卻覓不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:33.47,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}思念越發強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:37.59,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}無法傳達到這份祈願
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.64,0:00:44.18,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}一定是因為	迷失了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.85,0:00:51.90,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}無論何時  只有被映在這眼瞳裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:55.36,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}是唯一的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:00:58.53,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}一直如此堅信著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:02.70,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}世界並非唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.25,0:01:06.46,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}還有所謂如果的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:10.46,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}因為存在著無限可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:16.09,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}正迷失著方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.80,0:01:19.85,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}想要見你 卻覓不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:21.85,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}不論你現在身處何處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:25.06,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}必定能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:30.73,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}不慎闖入了瞳中的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:32.40,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:36.65,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}即使被黑暗之手遮蔽了去路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:40.78,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}即使被怯弱的心所迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:42.58,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}也不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:47.16,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}繼續尋找著

Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:31.21,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}会いたい 会えない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:33.47,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}思いつのるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:37.59,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}この祈りが届かないのは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.64,0:00:44.18,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}何かをきっと 見失ってるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.85,0:00:51.90,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}いつだって この瞳に 映されたものだけが
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:55.36,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}唯一の真実だと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:00:58.53,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}信じていたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:02.70,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}世界は一つじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.25,0:01:06.46,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}もしもという世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:10.46,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}無限にあるとして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:16.09,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}いま途方に暮れている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.80,0:01:19.85,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}会いたい 会えない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:21.85,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}いま何処にいるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:25.06,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}必ず見つけ出すから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:30.73,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}迷い込んだのは瞳の中にある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:32.40,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:36.65,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}例え暗闇がゆく手を遮り
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:40.78,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}弱気な心惑わせても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:42.58,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}諦めないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:47.16,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}探しつづけるから

Comment: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,【對白】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\fad(1200,1200)\be1\bord2\4a&Hc1&\3a&Hc1&\shad3\pos(505,372)}蜜爾佳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.59,0:02:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著 讓我們去看一看下一本書吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來在這個世界裏 好像發生過一點不幸的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭絲加勒絲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.99,0:02:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 戴上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛 蘭絲加勒絲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭絲加勒絲 你去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初美會在這種小島上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.00,0:03:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是小啊 是無人島吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那來這裡不是毫無意義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我先去偵察一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.39,0:03:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就剩我們兩人了呢 葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別發出那種怪聲 噁心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快累趴下了 不減肥不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊啊 你最好稍微減減肥 跟我一起去如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重啊 好重 真的好重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.76,0:04:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好重啊 果然是重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻鸚鵡全身的皮下脂肪高達100%
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想變成大胖子的話最好停手喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 快停手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.43,0:04:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭絲加勒絲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.44,0:04:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.73,0:04:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.71,0:04:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這隻虎是你的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我是莉莉絲 這位是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 你們要打蜜爾佳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.89,0:05:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會做那種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要欺負蜜爾佳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會欺負你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾佳住在這個島上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在島上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟誰一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞倫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞倫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞倫是蜜爾佳的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 像是在哪裡聽到過的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 莉莉絲也是朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成爲你的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麼想成爲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.94,0:05:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說做朋友什麼的 只會吃虧所以讓人討厭的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰這樣説的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了 是婆婆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個婆婆也是這個島上的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 以前在這個島上 現在不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 葉月是朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾佳的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.86,0:05:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾佳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼 剛才的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是“啪哩啪哩”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啪哩啪哩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.03,0:06:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 “啪哩啪哩”是會稍微有點痛的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.87,0:06:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾佳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 塞倫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾佳大人 您沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾佳今天也是沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:06:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幾位是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:07:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們想和蜜爾佳成爲朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以和他們成爲朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,0:07:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 難得各位來拜訪這個小島
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我作向導帶領各位去行宮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 葉月有戀人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要長大後就會有戀人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.84,0:07:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的戀人就是指男人 塞倫是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾佳從沒見過男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月見過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.59,0:07:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 見過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:08:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說男人都是很美妙的 是那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月是男人還是女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的 是女人 女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人的奶子不會鼓起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說葉月不是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣說很容易懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶子是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是乳房 関西腔裏叫奶子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾佳胸部沒有鼓起來 蜜爾佳是男人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.48,0:08:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等蜜爾佳長到這麼大時 就會變成“波波”的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時男人就會一個接一個追著你跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結婚對象什麼的可以隨你挑選
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:09:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好喝 真是好茶葉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.93,0:09:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道真的不記得我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有那頂帽子 還是讓人感到不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.44,0:09:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭絲加勒絲 重新向葉月打聲招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.63,0:09:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是那樣 那個孩子也真是古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.41,0:09:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是厲害 你是能夠明白的呢 蜜爾佳大人的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲蜜爾佳大人一直沒有長大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:09:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有長大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:10:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾佳大人從很多年以前開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個樣子沒有改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我之前負責教育蜜爾佳大人的人非常嚴格
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.99,0:10:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎每天都會很嚴厲地責罰蜜爾佳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那樣不知持續了多少年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲蜜爾佳大人一直保持著小孩子的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人後來去哪裡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一個年老的婆婆那裡聽到過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.03,0:10:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某一天 一件慘不忍睹的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個可怕的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事蜜爾佳知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想吃點心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.59,0:10:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果烤餅也可以的話 我可以做給你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 蜜爾佳好想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼帶我去廚房
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.49,0:10:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好聞的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月 你當我家裏的廚師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真正好吃的烤餅並不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.21,0:11:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經收到過全宇宙第一好吃的烤餅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 那個人就是葉月的戀人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.07,0:11:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.14,0:11:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲葉月説話時目光非常的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以蜜爾佳就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.17,0:11:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天來的真是一些不可思議的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭絲加勒絲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.74,0:12:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 莉莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.39,0:12:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結婚是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.85,0:12:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾佳大人 從哪裡聽到那種…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊那個古怪的鳥先生說的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是古怪的鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.53,0:12:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 就是跟男人卿卿我我 然後一直在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.99,0:12:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 就是這樣 到了晚上 慢慢地 慢慢地…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等蜜爾佳長大後 一定會有一個美好的婚姻的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾佳能長大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一定能的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 得想辦法先解決那個莫名其妙的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 蜜爾佳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在睡覺之前要先洗澡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大家一起去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好啊 一起去吧一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼 幹什麼 這種處置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底對我做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣呢 葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得這麼一次 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.98,0:13:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 稍後我一個人去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不用這麼害羞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉絲會去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說要在浴池裏 幫我教蜜爾佳大人從1數到100嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好啊 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 去洗澡的話要脫掉那個帽子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是 要脫掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.61,0:14:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是讓人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾佳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.84,0:14:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾佳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不要緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.28,0:14:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“啪哩啪哩”的原因我已經明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 蜜爾佳 去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.22,0:15:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.61,0:15:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾佳已經脫完了 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.25,0:15:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我的衣服脫起來比較費勁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麼這種時候卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.14,0:15:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你是怎麼到這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說都是靠毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.46,0:15:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個倒是有件好事情想要告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你是想去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.36,0:15:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接在這裡把禮服脫掉不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 這樣觸碰人家的背會讓人家有感覺的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是莉莉絲還是葉月還是塞倫胸部都好大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有蜜爾佳胸部平平的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.35,0:16:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無須擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人不只是胸部而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.37,0:16:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾佳今晚可以跟葉月一起睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 葉月的戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲那個人可以從葉月這裡得到很多的關心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.84,0:17:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻沒有人給蜜爾佳很多的關心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.05,0:17:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒我 婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天蜜爾佳違反了囑咐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天蜜爾佳說了謊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天蜜爾佳頂了嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天蜜爾佳在心裏面說了“婆婆去死”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾佳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9436
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9545
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9654
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9763
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.52,0:18:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9872
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9981
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 完成的非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於沒有一個錯誤 可以給一些獎勵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.89,0:18:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 想要什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.44,0:18:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾佳想要一個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.69,0:18:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一個戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.68,0:18:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話蜜爾佳就可以得到很多的關心 變得很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.56,0:19:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的 你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲使用了魔力而讓成長停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是隨便說說罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.04,0:19:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月是從哪裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.34,0:19:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遠 很遠的國家來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪個國家裏有什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.01,0:19:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西都有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是全都非常無趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.51,0:19:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡大概有多少人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多得讓人討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人跟女人都有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.33,0:19:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月爲何沒跟戀人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.29,0:19:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不在了 所以我正在找他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.44,0:19:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾佳也想去找找
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾佳的戀人在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.48,0:19:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定在這個海的對面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海的對面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.71,0:20:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又開始了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.98,0:20:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.65,0:20:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的“啪哩啪哩”比以往都要長 爲什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑鬼 停手 快停手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾佳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.96,0:20:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾佳要去海的對面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.42,0:21:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 蜜爾佳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.39,0:21:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾佳

Comment: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:33.84,jped,,0000,0000,0000,,【ED：永遠の祈りを捧げて】
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:41.65,jped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}永遠の祈りをささげて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:48.37,jped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}大事なもの諦めたりしない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:21:59.29,jped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}どんなに遠くても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.29,0:22:02.67,jped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}きっと捕まえてみせる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:10.43,jped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}君と僕との それが約束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:17.48,jped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}思いでも 抱きしめないでいても
